cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DC 

This paper focuses on improving spectrum resource utilization in a multi-access edge computing (MEC) in autonomous vehicular network (AVNET). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper involves optimization problems, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with control and management of the network, which could place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
